In PCM mode the start of frame is indicated by a rising edge.
WS is HIGH.
In PCM mode the start of frame is indicated by a falling edge.</description>
              <bitOffset>13</bitOffset>
              <bitWidth>1</bitWidth>
              <access>read-write</access>
