Writing 1 to this flag clears the SEDC bit in the RAMCFG_MxISR register. Reading this flag returns the SEDC value.</description>
              <bitOffset>0</bitOffset>
              <bitWidth>1</bitWidth>
              <access>read-write</access>
            </field>
            <field>
