Set and reset by software to control the frequency of the pll2_r_ck clock.
These bits can be written only when the PLL1 is disabled (PLL2ON = 0 and PLL2RDY = 0).
...</description>
              <bitOffset>24</bitOffset>
              <bitWidth>7</bitWidth>
              <access>read-write</access>
